Parkchester Apartments

Parkchester is a completely self contained community within the city. Comfort, convenience and affordability are the hallmarks of every no fee apartment. Rentals for one bedroom apartments start as low as $1290 per month; $1600 for two bedroom apartments, and $1900 for a three-bedroom

What We Suggest

Amenities & Facilities

The complex has more than 100 retail outlets including Macy's, Applebee's, Starbucks, our own medical and dental offices, most major banks and much more. Public, private, and parochial schools are nearby. Other amenities include onsite management, convenient garages as well as on-street parking and roving 24-hour security.
